8-01-30T00:28:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b640e5152cdbbfe6b5286ba7e789cec9a9378cdd","tid":544682,"uid":120123,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T00:31:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唱反調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正宗連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 型撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>唔係特登唱反調，只係覺得隻game複雜左好多，由其是個地圖，勁多層。兜左成個鐘就好想嘔，玩慣舊mh簡單直接屠龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得隻game已經簡化咗好多囉喎...<br />\n以前你如果要搵隻龍嘅話, 一係你有熱氣球, 一係你就記得隻龍一開始嚮邊. <br />\n<br />\n如果唔係一樣搵到你仆街, 同埋今集隻龍你唔使再掟著色玉都可以追蹤到佢嘛, 同埋你話好多層啫, 但係你又有地圖嘛, <br />\n你又見到曬個地圖邊一度有啲乜嘢採集, 我覺得今集簡單好多"},{"pid":"7a612da97a0aa2ae3cdd945eb2f834f444092d73","tid":544682,"uid":1888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T00:33:48.000Z","msg":"咁都叫複雜左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佩服"},{"pid":"0c94c83dd72132cacbb9204b6f145d053709cadc","tid":544682,"uid":67792,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T00:38:39.000Z","msg":"我諗緊有咩打手會可以攻擊MH而得益？"},{"pid":"83d8e90dd0a9e0b89d237c3fbba60024fc7bb0c0","tid":544682,"uid":7988,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0c94c83dd72132cacbb9204b6f145d053709cadc","tid":544682,"uid":67792,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T00:38:39.000Z","msg":"我諗緊有咩打手會可以攻擊MH而得益？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T01:53:30.000Z","msg":"唔通一定要一致好評？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c30bc69e49dff74b5ad537862c646415c9cd82","tid":544682,"uid":7988,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"b640e5152cdbbfe6b5286ba7e789cec9a9378cdd","tid":544682,"uid":120123,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTi